data.description: ***Offer Deadline Tuesday 11/21 @ 5:00pm*** Adorable Open Concept Craftsman Bungalow with charm and character, hardwood floors under carpet, and beautiful woodwork throughout featuring spacious living room with brick wood burning fireplace separated by decorative built-ins, fully applianced eat-in kitchen with peninsula and pantry, big full bathroom and 3 good sized bedrooms. Plus, full unfinished basement with woodstove, work bench and laundry with utility sink, public water and sewer, replaced roof, huge wraparound farmer’s porch, 1 car detached garage, paved driveway, and low maintenance backyard all on lovely lot in great West side neighborhood. Could use some TLC but has tons of potential. See floorplan, 3D tour, video walk through and showing packet for additional info. Private showings welcome.
